.mb-3
  %h3.mb-4.fs-4 Metadata
  %p.text-muted
    This dataset uses the 
    = link_to 'Open Energy Metadata (OEMetadata)', 'https://openenergyplatform.github.io/oemetadata/latest/', target: '_blank'
    standard.
    %h4.fs-6.mt-4 Want to know more about the metadata process?
    %p
      = link_to user_guide_path(anchor: 'faq'), class: 'text-decoration-none icon-link icon-link-hover align-items-baseline' do
        %span Learn more about the Metadata
        %i.bi.bi-arrow-right
  .border.rounded.bg-light-subtle.p-4.d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.align-items-start.justify-content-between.gap-3{'data-controller' => 'copy'}

    / Button: first on small screens, last on md+, right-aligned when stacked
    %button.btn.btn-outline-secondary.btn-sm.d-inline-flex.order-0.order-md-1.ms-auto.ms-md-3.align-self-start{'data-action' => 'click->copy#copy', 'data-copy-target' => 'button'}
      %i.bi.bi-clipboard.me-1{'data-copy-target' => 'icon'}
      %span{'data-copy-target' => 'label'} Copy

    / Pre: second on small screens, first on md+
    %pre.mb-0.flex-grow-1.w-100.overflow-auto.order-1.order-md-0(style="word-break: break-word;")
      %code.d-block{'data-copy-target' => 'source'}= JSON.pretty_generate(metadatum.data)
  